rComments: It was an engineering elective for me and the professor was alot of fun even though the course is tooo boring..veru helpful guy and very understanding if u cannot submit an assignment or something on time..go through his lectures and the textbook..midterms were easy..final was a killer..bottomline: good prof but u have to study

Loves what he teaches. Nice coherent but boring lectures. The lecture notes you have to buy are so small and he doesn't post them online due to copyright. Midterms were easy, final was brutal. Do every question in the assignment, even though you hand it in a group. only 4 labs throughout the semester, biomed students like me have 12 extra ones.
nice, young prof. Not that great at teaching, but tries very hard to make sure everyone understands the imporant points. Outlines what's on quizzes and midterm/final very clearly!!
Excellent Instructor. I'm very glad I got this guys and his TA's. Very laid back, very helpful, and presents the course in a very good manner. Good job Kris, keep up the good work.
